data.name: EditTime
desc: specifies service of a text field that provides information about the duration the document has been edited.

properties.name: CurrentPresentation
desc: contains the current content of the text field.
This property is especially useful for import/export purposes.

properties.name: DateTimeValue
desc: contains the date and time as double value.

properties.name: IsFixed
desc: If this flag is set to false the author will be overridden by the current author each time the document is saved.
If this flag is set to FALSE the date or time is always displayed as the current date or time.

properties.name: IsFixedLanguage
desc: determines whether changes in language attributes at the position the text field is located also change the number format as appropriate for this language.

properties.name: NumberFormat
desc: this is the number format for this field.
